coba.sql: SELECT 2+2 AS TAMBAH, 3-1 AS KURANG, 4*5 AS KALI, 20/4 AS BAGI, 10/2 AS BAGI2

check_oss.sql:
select 'oss' as source, "date", count(distinct file_name) as count_filename, count(*) as total, sum(file_size)/1024/1024 as file_size, max(ingest_at) as ingest_at
        from interconnection_source.oss_ran_source_sftp orss2 
        where ingest_at >= date(now()) - 10 and date >= date(now()) - 10
        group by 2
        order by 2 desc;
